  "summary": "Minecraft has another glitch",
  "description": "## Near Broken, Full Durability Tools\\n\\n#### On 5/8/25 I went into my Hermitcraft season 9 wold And My netherite tools had their Durability bars looking like they were going to break\\n\\nwith another use, I'm certain that I rarely used them, on my previous play session. I thought The game was just having a moment, so i tried repairing\\n\\nthem to full  Durability, I checked my old armor and tools that had been used and they had the durability glitch. sorry for bothering you and thank you for  \\n\\nmaking a game as great  Minecraft Congrats and Thank you for taking your time to read this report. \\n\\n\\n\\n",
